                  <interp inst="t18190421-240-crimeloc1342" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18190421-240-off1339 t18190421-240-crimeloc1342"></join>. I was crossing the road, and saw the prisoner with two coats under his arm. I ran in, and missed my father's coats from behind the door; I pursued him, calling Stop thief! and a gentleman stopped him. I am certain he is the man.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190421-240-person2246">
                  SUSAN 
                  POWELL
               <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2246" type="surname" value="POWELL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2246" type="given" value="SUSAN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2246" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . The prisoner ran by me with the coats under his arm; the last witness called Stop thief! he jumped into the hedge of a garden, left the coats there, and returned without them. The constable stopped him. I never lost sight of him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18190421-240-person2247">
                  THOMAS 
                  GOODWIN
               <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2247" type="surname" value="GOODWIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2247" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18190421-240-person2247" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a constable. I stopped the prisoner, who was running in Grove-street. He said there was nothing amiss, it was only a joke; I took him back and found the coats in the hedge.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I saw a man run into the garden with a bundle, and pursued him, but lost him.</p>
               <p>
